text: Gerry Sinnott (born 31 July 1951) is an Irish equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Irish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Ireland Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
